es interviews with him and several stanford students who have accompanied him on these trips over three decades wise has spent several weeks each year in the same poverty stricken region of guatemala providing basic health care watch the video paul wise at work in guatemala search chp search within everything courses events fellowships news op eds people publications research other pages news of interest core faculty member douglas owens receives national recognition august 31 2010 news shp core faculty paul wise blends medicine politics to improve health of guatemala's poorest video+ july 22 2010 chp pcor fsi stanford news in podcast economist victor fuchs discusses why a government sponsored insurance system won t work june 18 2009 news in news article wise discusses debate among doctors on treating very premature infants march 22 2006 in the news in magazine articles wise discusses lack of policy attention to kids health needs march 3 2006 in the news article highlights wise's work providing care medical education in guatemala january 27 2006 in the news support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 736 0815 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
